OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisposable vapes to be     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbanned for child health    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disposable vapes are set to be banned  
OL,6, as part of plans to tackle the rising  
OL,7, number of young people taking up       
OL,8, vaping, the government says.           
OL,10,FMeasures will also be introduced to    
OL,11,Fprevent vapes being marketed at        
OL,12,Fchildren and to target under age sales.
OL,14,FFigures from the Action on Smoking and 
OL,15,FHealth (Ash) charity suggest 7.6% of 11
OL,16,Fto 17-year-olds now vape regularly or  
OL,17,Foccasionally, up from 4.1% in 2020.    
OL,19,FThe ban is expected to be introduced   
OL,20,Facross the UK, the government said.    
